{"id":1495,"date":"2024-08-09T19:33:19","date_gmt":"2024-08-09T19:33:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1495"},"modified":"2024-08-09T20:03:50","modified_gmt":"2024-08-09T20:03:50","slug":"tm071-stone-edge","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm071-stone-edge\/","title":{"rendered":"TM071 Stone Edge"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM071 Stone Edge<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Found in the Crystal Peak 1F, near the entrance to Cube Corp. It requires Rock Climb and the yellow crystals should be powered off.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>The foe is stabbed by sharpened stones. It has a high critical-hit ratio.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>5<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Rock<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h3>Prerequisites<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Crystal Peak<\/li>\n<li>Complete the Crystal Peak section of the main story<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm08-rock-climb\/\">Rock Climb<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm06-rock-smash\/\">Rock Smash<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm07-waterfall\/\">Waterfall<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Location<\/h3>\n<p>Enter Crystal Peak and follow the linear path going forward.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-forward-in-crystal-peak.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path forward in Crystal Peak. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Following the path forward in Crystal Peak.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Smash the breakable rocks blocking your path and use the ladder behind them to go deeper into the cave.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-using-the-ladder-to-go-down.jpg\" alt=\"Using the ladder to go down. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Using the ladder to go down.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Use Surf to continue going forward.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-using-surf-to-continue-forward.jpg\" alt=\"Using Surf to continue forward. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Using Surf to continue forward.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Turn North to reach the area with interactable crystals.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-surfing-toward-the-area-with-interactable-crystals.jpg\" alt=\"Surfing toward the area with interactable crystals. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Surfing toward the area with interactable crystals.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Disable the yellow crystals while ensuring the other two crystals are enabled.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-disabling-the-yellow-crystals.jpg\" alt=\"Disabling the yellow crystals. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Disabling the yellow crystals.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>With the interactable crystal part done, go back and take the ladder to your East to go to the higher level.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-climbing-the-ladder-to-the-upper-floor.jpg\" alt=\"Climbing the ladder to the upper floor. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Climbing the ladder to the upper floor.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Use Rock Climb and Surf to go South on the water, then turn East to land on the platform with the stairs.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/07-pokemon-unbound-surfing-to-the-east-platform.jpg\" alt=\"Surfing to the East platform. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Surfing to the East platform.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Instead of climbing the stairs, use Rock Climb to scale the wall with blue crystals and follow the path South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/08-pokemon-unbound-climbing-the-wall-and-going-south.jpg\" alt=\"Climbing the wall and going South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Climbing the wall and going South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see some water to your South \u2013 Surf here to keep going south.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/09-pokemon-unbound-using-surf-to-continue-south.jpg\" alt=\"Using Surf to continue South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Using Surf to continue South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Use Waterfall to continue on the path and land on the platform to your East.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/10-pokemon-unbound-descending-from-a-waterfall.jpg\" alt=\"Descending from a waterfall. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Descending from a waterfall.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Keep going South until you see a pathway to your East.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/11-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-pathway-east.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the pathway East. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Taking the pathway East.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>In this new area, use Rock Climb to continue going East.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/12-pokemon-unbound-using-rock-climb-to-go-east.jpg\" alt=\"Using Rock Climb to go East. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Using Rock Climb to go East.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>On the way, you\u2019ll see some red crystals you can use Rock Climb on. Climb them and start following the path North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/13-pokemon-unbound-climbing-the-wall-and-following-the-path.jpg\" alt=\"Climbing the wall and following the path. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Climbing the wall and following the path.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll have to cross a blue and white bridge, indicating you\u2019re on the right path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/14-pokemon-unbound-crossing-the-blue-and-white-bridge.jpg\" alt=\"Crossing the blue and white bridge. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Crossing the blue and white bridge.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The TM for Stone Edge is at the end of the path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/15-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-tm-for-stone-edge-on-the-ground.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the TM for Stone Edge on the ground. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption class=\"caption\">Finding the TM for Stone Edge on the ground.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1496,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-1495","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1495","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1496"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1495"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1495"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}